data.description: AMAZING DEAL! NEW ROOF with SOLAR PANELS AND a new WATER SOFTENER are INCLUDED with this well priced home. This is a $40K + EXTRA value! The electric bill in this brutal heat has been a mere $55/month compared to a minimum of $268/month. This means $200 + can go towards your monthly mortgage payment!  Welcome to this charming two-story home nestled on a large corner lot. With its spacious interior, three bedrooms, two and a half bathrooms, this property offers a comfortable and stylish living experience. As you approach the home, you'll notice its well-maintained exterior. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. Natural light pours in through large windows, creating an airy ambiance and illuminating the freshly painted walls. The kitchen is a chef's delight, showcasing modern appliances, sleek countertops, and ample cabinet space. Whether you're entertaining guests or preparing meals for your loved ones, this kitchen offers both functionality and style. The master suite is a true retreat, offering a generous walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom with double vanities, a luxurious soaking tub, and a separate shower. The additional bedrooms are well-sized and offer plenty of space for family members. And the game room is a fantastic addition for entertainment and relaxation.
